Edit /etc/inetd.conf and add this line:

telnet   stream  tcp  nowait  root.telnetd  /usr/sbin/tcpd \
	/usr/sbin/in.telnetd  -L ${PREFIX}/sbin/ttysnoops

Spool directory is: ${VARBASE}/spool/ttysnoop

===========================================================================
